Avoiding the line

Ernesto Carrella

January 24, 2017

This is the first of the 3 demos we need to resubmit the ABM synthesis paper. Here we have two species of fish, red all over the map and blue in the middle. Both sell for 10$ a unit. We place an MPA on the area where blue fish live but the MPA isnt perfect (that is, it doesnt cover the entire area where blue fish live).
